Show HN: Kay, ChatGPT Inside WhatsApp
text:
Kay uses the new ChatGPT API.

Benefits:

- no login needed

- accessible from your phone (easier to use compared to the web interface)

- available in a familiar interface (WhatsApp on mobile and Desktop)

Privacy:

- your WhatsApp id and the last 4 messages (back and forth) are stored, as needed to provided a conversational experience.

- the data is stored on Firestore.
